      <h2>About Ferni</h2>
      <p class="body-lg">Ferni is a voice-first AI life coaching platform featuring six specialized AI personas who work together to support personal growth. Available 24/7 via web, phone, or API.</p>
      
      <div class="press-boilerplate">
        <h3>Boilerplate</h3>
        <p>Ferni is six brilliant minds that remember your whole story and show up at 2am with the same presence as noon. With specialized personas—Ferni (life coach), Nayan (wisdom), Peter (research), Alex (communication), Maya (habits), and Jordan (planning)—you get guidance that evolves with you. Ferni remembers every conversation, responds in under 500ms, and can be reached by simply calling a phone number. Based in Park City, Utah, Ferni is on a mission to give everyone access to the kind of support that was once reserved for the privileged few.</p>
